title: Close Encounters Down Under
overview: The most comprehensive investigation into close encounters in Australia and New Zealand ever undertaken.Revealing untold stories of UFO sightings, abductions, and other paranormal events, Close Encounters Down Under is a spine-tingling investigation into some of the most bizarre alien encounters of all time.Â From the alps of New Zealand to the rugged Australian Outback, every episode is packed with rare footage, recently declassified archives, and chilling first-hand accounts.Eyewitnesses, experts, and eccentrics weigh in on everything from recent events, decades-old mysteries, and ancient lore as they share eerie tales of the most popular extraterrestrial hotspot on Earth.
